<para id="fs-id1167834130933"><emphasis effect="bold">Apply Geometric Sequences and Series in the Real World</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-id1167834130939">In the following exercises, solve the problem.</para>
<exercise id="fs-id1167834130942" class="material-set-2">
<problem id="fs-id1167834130944">
<para id="fs-id1167834130946">Find the total effect on the economy of each government tax rebate to each household in order to stimulate the economy if each household will spend the indicated percent of the rebate in goods and services.</para>
